   GENLIST Theorems:
   GENLIST_0           |- !f. GENLIST f 0 = []
   GENLIST_1           |- !f. GENLIST f 1 = [f 0]
   GENLIST_EQ          |- !f1 f2 n. (!m. m < n ==> f1 m = f2 m) ==> GENLIST f1 n = GENLIST f2 n
   GENLIST_EQ_NIL      |- !f n. (GENLIST f n = []) <=> (n = 0)
   GENLIST_LAST        |- !f n. LAST (GENLIST f (SUC n)) = f n
