(* Proof: by induction on n.
   Base case: !a b. SUM (GENLIST a 0) + SUM (GENLIST b 0) = SUM (GENLIST (\k. a k + b k) 0)
     Since GENLIST f 0 = []    by GENLIST
       and SUM [] = 0          by SUM_NIL
