     = SUM (GENLIST a n) + SUM (GENLIST b n) + (a n + b n)    by arithmetic
     = SUM (GENLIST (\k. a k + b k) n) + (a n + b n)          by induction hypothesis
     = SUM (GENLIST (\k. a k + b k) (SUC n))                  by SUM_DECOMPOSE_LAST
