       n * (n ** 2) * (n ** 4) * ... * (n ** (2 ** (m - 1)))
     = n ** (1 + 2 + 4 + ... + 2 ** (m - 1))
     = n ** (2 ** m - 1)

   By induction on m.
   Base: PROD (GENLIST (\j. n ** 2 ** j) 0) = n ** (2 ** 0 - 1)
      LHS = PROD (GENLIST (\j. n ** 2 ** j) 0)
          = PROD []                by GENLIST_0
          = 1                      by PROD
      RHS = n ** (1 - 1)           by EXP_0
