       = SUM [1 .. n'] - SUM [1 .. m - 1]     by listRangeINC_SUM
       = SUM [1 .. n'] - SUM [1 .. m']        by m' = m - 1
       = SUM [1 ..< n] - SUM [1 ..< m]        by listRangeLHI_to_listRangeINC
