     (t ** n - 1) = (t - 1) * (1 + t + t ** 2 + ... + t ** (n-1))
  or  1 + t + t ** 2 + ... + t ** (n - 1) = (t ** n - 1) DIV (t - 1),
  which is the sum of the geometric series.
